I am always interested in Quality, Unique, High Grade, Commemorative, Limited Edition, Tactical, Colt, Winchester, S&W, and out of production firearms in original excellent to new condition. I rarely accept current production, customs, or very common guns on trade. If you have a quality modern firearm you seldom see in most Gun Shops priced with my resale in mind I will probably be interested in it. Email me a very detailed description of your firearm or if you have more than one email a list with a detailed description and pricing or an idea of how much you need to get out of your trade or trades. Please do not be afraid to tell me about your trade and all you have with it, remember I only know what you tell me. Include a price and photos if possible. I will not answer emails if they are not detailed. Email us prior to bidding about trading do not bid first then try to negotiate a trade. If your trade is worth more we will pay you the difference. Information on how we handle direct purchases will be emailed to you should you have something we are interested in purchasing. QUESTIONS/CONCERNS: Please submit all correspondence via email using the Armslist.com system and be sure your information listed with Armslist.com is current. Verify you are able to receive emails from the Armslist.com service. Spam blockers, firewalls, etc. I can answer most questions within a very short period of time. SHIPPING/HANDLING: USA sales only, no exceptions! We ship using UPS or USPS and all shipments are sent insured to the amount you bid. Handguns ship 2 Day Air and Long Guns ship Ground. The shipping amount is posted on this listing and will be in addition to the amount you bid or the buy now price. ALL firearms must ship to a FFL Dealer or if the firearm qualifies we will accept a C&R. ALL Non Firearms will ship to the name and address you have listed with Armslist.com The shipping rate posting in this listing is for the Continental USA only, Birmingham and Hawaii rates are available upon request. We can ship your purchase within 48 hours of receipt of verified funds. This means the payment you send must clear our bank first, this may take up to 4 business days depending on your payment form. We are a FFL Licensed Dealer and we will include a copy of our FFL License with a firearm purchase to your dealer of choice. We ship any non firearm to the name and address you have listed with Armslist.com or the credit card holder. Warranty/Inspection Period: We do not handle, sell, or trade junk. All of our listings are advertised in true form, we take a lot of photos from multiple angles using natural light. We do not photo shop or alter the appearance of the firearm however we do remove serial numbers or change them electronically on most all listings for security reasons. We own every listing posted, we do not try to sell guns not in our inventory. I have no reason to mislead you nor do I want angry customers. Sales are final and sold AS IS unless approved by me. We do not offer any inspection periods. All firearms should be checked over by your Gunsmith prior to being shot or handled. In the event a firearm has to be returned to us the shipping and Armslist.com fees are never refundable under any circumstances. PLEASE know your own state and local laws prior to bidding. I will not modify any weapon to make it legal for your state. I will ship to all states if you have a FFL Dealer who will receive the item as it is listed without modification or disassembly. Thank you for taking the time to view our listing and I look forward to offering you a safe, fast and friendly transaction.
